dct_title_s: (East coast of Africa) The slave caravan route from Dar-es-Salam to Kilwa to accompany the paper by Captn. F. Elton
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Author's route shown in red. Includes information on vegetation and crop and copal production. Approximate locations of districts and tribal territories are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 44 (1874), pp. 227-52; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 44 1874
